# Prisma Migration Placeholder
#
# Actual migration files are generated automatically by Prisma.
# Run the following to create your first migration:
#
#   npx prisma migrate dev --name init
#
# This will:
# 1. Introspect your schema.prisma
# 2. Create a SQL migration file in this directory
# 3. Apply the migration to your database
# 4. Generate the Prisma Client
